snippet.title: A Pixel Beat 'em up Game: "I Am The Hero". Download on the App Store
snippet.description: I Am The Hero is a pixel art, beat 'em up, fighting game that tells the story of a "Hero" with a glorious but mysterious past. Is he the hero he thinks he is or is there another side to this legendary figure?
